      "category": "NEWS",
      "date": "Feb 10, 2026",
      "html": "<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3554d5e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3554d5e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Artist Call Open SX Festival 2026</span></p>\n<p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">We are now officially open for artist submissions for SX Festival 2026.</span></p>\n<p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">SX Festival is a space for expression, radical creativity, and immersive artistic experiences. We welcome artists who challenge boundaries, explore intimacy, movement, sound, identity, and the human body in innovative ways.</span></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f30e1e9 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"f30e1e9\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-257a48a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"257a48a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-edb9cd7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"edb9cd7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"347\" height=\"347\" src=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph31.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-780\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph31.webp 347w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph31-300x300-2.webp 300w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph31-150x150-2.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 347px) 100vw, 347px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4c3904a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"4c3904a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e2853a elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"2e2853a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"347\" height=\"347\" src=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph31-1.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-779\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph31-1.webp 347w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph31-1-300x300-2.webp 300w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph31-1-150x150-2.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 347px) 100vw, 347px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e1765e0 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e1765e0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7a6b7af elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"7a6b7af\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"347\" height=\"347\" src=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph32.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-778\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph32.webp 347w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph32-300x300-2.webp 300w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph32-150x150-2.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 347px) 100vw, 347px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b0980a2 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"b0980a2\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f70ed0f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f70ed0f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">We want to grow together with you and share this journey as partners. As a Brand Ambassador, you will receive a starter package with a value of 800 EUR in goods and VIP entries. You will also have the opportunity to monetize through ticket sales and enjoy priority access to VIP seats before anyone else.</span></p>\n<p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">If this resonates with you, apply by completing the </span><a class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-underline text-strikethrough-none\" draggable=\"false\" href=\"https://wkf.ms/49zQjCt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">application form.</a></p>\n<p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Our team will review all submissions and get back to you within seven working days from the moment we receive your application. If selected, we will personally contact you and guide you through the onboarding process.</span></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-495aa8d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"495aa8d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3489908 elementor-mobile-align-justify elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"3489908\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">join our<br />newsletter</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d7b51eb elementor-mobile-align-justify elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"d7b51eb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">BECOME A SPONSOR</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>"
